:"九年，唔夠十一年嗰位巴打勁<br />\n<br />\n不過，提醒大家唔好浪費時間同心力，我自己宜家都只係二字出頭，仲有大把青春，大把機會發展事業同自我增值。<br />\n男仔十幾歳除非靚仔、有錢、口才好，要溝女其實唔易，雙方bargaining power差太遠，單戀個女仔係唔會俾反應你，因為佢年輕時仲可以慢慢等。<br />\n<br />\n兩性差異導致女性要慢慢挑選對象，男性就要大海撈針。作為男性，應該拓展社交圈子，慢慢試探出對你有興趣既女性，再進一步發展。對你無興趣既女性，可以直接飛過。"},{"pid":"1b7b14099aeea4b719cc9e2849720cb3ac1f3d7c","tid":1171080,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T14:07:50.000Z","msg":"淨係知緣可以狙擊條女好撚耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b3bd49507e8d732e56d802a2b1ff0c853055872","tid":1171080,"uid":25237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T14:09:30.000Z","msg":"四年 <br />\n但依個月終於move on咗 可以用返朋友嘅身分同佢相處"},{"pid":"ae07cb99b97c7c8aaf534a9ad0b3f16e5e23e952","tid":1171080,"uid":43041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"08f903f24ef3e3724588ccd3333d689889e47baa","tid":1171080,"uid":120930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"397d16183db81ef084adf983e423d4ec5b877acc","tid":1171080,"uid":43041,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T13:05:20.000Z","msg":"十一年"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T13:32:48.000Z","msg":"出現了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T18:38:27.000Z","msg":"已修成正果，結左婚"},{"pid":"f173de547d1a05fc3998f0913155f78ede8c6421","tid":1171080,"uid":152123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ae07cb99b97c7c8aaf534a9ad0b3f16e5e23e952","tid":1171080,"uid":43041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"08f903f24ef3e3724588ccd3333d689889e47baa","tid":1171080,"uid":120930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"397d16183db81ef084adf983e423d4ec5b877acc","tid":1171080,"uid":43041,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T13:05:20.000Z","msg":"十一年"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T13:32:48.000Z","msg":"出現了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"